LANG
====
   inherit

DESCRIPTION
===========
      KEYWORD
      =======
      DESCRIPTION
      ===========
      SYNTAX
      ======
      DESCRIPTION
      ===========
   The inherit statement specifies that the present object will inherit 
   functionality from the object at <path>. The concept of inheritance (and 
   thus the inherit statement) is explained in detail in inheritance(C).

SEE ALSO
========
   inheritance(C)
